<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 10:05:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>船倾覆后，三名罗兴亚难民被发现死在海中</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/three-rohingya-refugees-found-dead-in-sea-after-boat-capsizes/articleshow/108748530.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108748530.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;亚齐附近的搜寻工作结束，发现三具罗辛亚难民尸体。 75名获救人员被转移。班达亚齐搜救机构负责人、难民署工作人员协助确认死者身份。 70 名失踪或死亡的罗兴亚难民引发担忧。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 09:55:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/three-rohingya-refugees-found-dead-in-sea-after-boat-capsizes/articleshow/108748530.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦：遏制非法烟草贸易是国际货币基金组织提供资金的关键条件</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-curbing-illicit-tobacco-trade-a-key-condition-for-funding-by-imf/articleshow/108748346.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108748346.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 09:54:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-curbing-illicit-tobacco-trade-a-key-condition-for-funding-by-imf/articleshow/108748346.cms</guid></item><item><title>比拉瓦尔·布托在胡里节向巴基斯坦的印度教社区致以祝福</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/bilawal-bhutto-wishes-hindu-community-in-pakistan-on-holi/articleshow/108748163.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108748163.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦前外交部长比拉瓦尔·布托在洒红节向该国的印度教社区致以祝福，声称这一节日提醒人们超越宗教或文化差异的共同人性。巴基斯坦人民党（PPP）主席在一份声明中强调了促进包容性和尊重国内多元文化传统的重要性。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 09:05:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/bilawal-bhutto-wishes-hindu-community-in-pakistan-on-holi/articleshow/108748163.cms</guid></item><item><title>波兰武装部队称俄罗斯在袭击乌克兰时侵犯了波兰领空</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-violates-polands-air-space-in-attack-on-ukraine-polands-armed-forces-say/articleshow/108748367.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108748367.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;波兰武装部队报告称，俄罗斯周日早些时候向乌克兰西部的目标发射了一枚巡航导弹，侵犯了其领空。武装部队在社交媒体平台X上表示：“3月24日凌晨4点23分，俄罗斯联邦远程航空夜间发射的一枚巡航导弹侵犯了波兰领空。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 09:16:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-violates-polands-air-space-in-attack-on-ukraine-polands-armed-forces-say/articleshow/108748367.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯对基辅发动空袭，乌克兰防空回应</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-conducts-air-strike-on-kyiv-ukraines-air-defence-responds/articleshow/108743711.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108743711.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰官员报告称，俄罗斯对基辅发动空袭，但遭到乌克兰防空系统的反击。市长克里琴科证实首都发生爆炸，军队正在参与防御。目击者听到爆炸声并看到空中武器被拦截。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 04:26:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-conducts-air-strike-on-kyiv-ukraines-air-defence-responds/articleshow/108743711.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯谴责俄罗斯恐怖袭击事件引发网上批评</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-condemns-terror-attack-in-russia-sparking-online-criticism/articleshow/108747079.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108747079.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈马斯领导人向俄罗斯最近发生的恐怖袭击事件的受害者表示哀悼，莫斯科附近有 133 人丧生。伊斯兰国-呼罗珊声称对此负责。尽管与以色列发生冲突，哈马斯仍然支持俄罗斯。哈马斯在激进组织关系复杂的情况下谴责暴力行为，网上批评者质疑其诚意。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 08:11:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-condemns-terror-attack-in-russia-sparking-online-criticism/articleshow/108747079.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员透露美国与哈马斯交换人质囚犯的提议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-official-reveals-us-proposal-for-hostage-prisoner-exchange-with-hamas/articleshow/108747296.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108747296.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国在以巴谈判中提出了一项囚犯交换计划，涉及哈马斯释放的被监禁的巴勒斯坦人和人质。中央情报局局长威廉·伯恩斯（William Burns）促进了在汇率问题上存在分歧的谈判。以色列同意美国的过渡提议，等待哈马斯的回应。停战谈判旨在停止加沙攻势并从最近发生的事件中解救人质。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 08:21:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-official-reveals-us-proposal-for-hostage-prisoner-exchange-with-hamas/articleshow/108747296.cms</guid></item><item><title>致命的食肉细菌感染在日本迅速蔓延</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/deadly-flesh-eating-bacterial-infection-spreading-rapidly-in-japan/articleshow/108746395.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108746395.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一种致命的食肉细菌感染——链球菌中毒性休克综合症（STSS），死亡率高达30%，正在日本迅速蔓延。美国国家传染病研究所披露，2023 年确诊病例为 941 例，2024 年病例数将继续激增。医学专家建议保持卫生习惯以防止其传播。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 08:08:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/deadly-flesh-eating-bacterial-infection-spreading-rapidly-in-japan/articleshow/108746395.cms</guid></item><item><title>塞尔维亚人对特朗普家族就北约爆炸地点达成的协议感到愤怒</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/serbians-angry-at-trump-family-deal-for-site-of-nato-bombing/articleshow/108745957.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108745957.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 07:57:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/serbians-angry-at-trump-family-deal-for-site-of-nato-bombing/articleshow/108745957.cms</guid></item><item><title>200多名尼日利亚学生在卡杜纳北部被绑架后获释</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/more-than-200-nigerian-students-released-after-abduction-in-northern-kaduna/articleshow/108746198.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108746198.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;卡杜纳州长办公室周日证实，距离 69 万美元赎金截止日期仅几天，在尼日利亚北部被绑架的 200 多名学生和教职员工已获释，安然无恙。这起事件于 3 月 7 日在卡杜纳州库里加发生，这是该国自 2021 年以来首次发生大规模绑架事件，当时一所高中有 150 多名学生被绑架。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 07:40:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/more-than-200-nigerian-students-released-after-abduction-in-northern-kaduna/articleshow/108746198.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴西一名女孩在风暴造成至少 12 人死亡 16 小时后从废墟中撤离</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/a-girl-in-brazil-recused-from-rubble-after-16-hours-as-storm-kills-at-least-12/articleshow/108745025.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108745025.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴西东南部因暴风雨导致房屋倒塌，一名小女孩被困在废墟下16个多小时，最终被成功救出。可悲的是，女孩的父亲发现她身旁已无生命迹象，于是用自己的身体保护了她。风暴造成了毁灭性的损失，导致当局向里约热内卢州的山区派遣救援队。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 06:43:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/a-girl-in-brazil-recused-from-rubble-after-16-hours-as-storm-kills-at-least-12/articleshow/108745025.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦外长表示“认真”考虑恢复与印度的贸易关系</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/seriously-considering-trade-ties-restoration-with-india-says-pakistan-foreign-minister/articleshow/108744325.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108744325.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦外交部长穆罕默德·伊沙克·达尔表示愿意认真考虑恢复与印度的贸易关系，该关系自 2019 年 8 月以来一直处于搁置状态。在因废除第 370 条而紧张之后，这一立场标志着巴基斯坦对印度的外交态度可能发生转变。坚称印度必须扭转其在克什米尔的行动，以此作为对话的先决条件，但印度拒绝了这一要求</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 05:31:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/seriously-considering-trade-ties-restoration-with-india-says-pakistan-foreign-minister/articleshow/108744325.cms</guid></item><item><title>德国面临人力短缺，大学生成为电车运营商</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/university-students-become-tram-operators-as-germany-faces-manpower-shortage/articleshow/108743993.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108743993.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 05:24:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/university-students-become-tram-operators-as-germany-faces-manpower-shortage/articleshow/108743993.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国油轮在也门海域遭胡塞武装袭击</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/chinese-owned-oil-tanker-attacked-off-yemen-by-houthi-rebels/articleshow/108743593.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108743593.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国军方表示，周六，一艘中国油轮在也门附近遭到胡塞武装发射的弹道导弹袭击，胡塞武装加强了对红海航运的打击。中央司令部表示，胡塞叛军在黄浦号附近的红海发射了四枚反舰弹道导弹，随后第五枚击中了该船。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 04:05:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/chinese-owned-oil-tanker-attacked-off-yemen-by-houthi-rebels/articleshow/108743593.cms</guid></item><item><title>西班牙：法官下令全国封锁 Telegram</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/spain-judge-orders-telegram-to-be-blocked-nationwide/articleshow/108743236.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108743236.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 03:45:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/spain-judge-orders-telegram-to-be-blocked-nationwide/articleshow/108743236.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国秘书长古特雷斯访问加沙边境，以色列称联合国为“反以色列机构”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-calls-un-anti-israeli-body-as-un-chief-guterres-visits-gaza-border/articleshow/108743229.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108743229.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周六，以色列外交部长批评联合国秘书长安东尼奥·古特雷斯，指责联合国是安东尼奥·古特雷斯领导下的“反以色列机构”。​​古特雷斯在访问加沙边境期间呼吁停火，国际社会的冲突日益加剧。以色列和哈马斯冲突导致该地区平民伤亡和人道主义危机令人担忧。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 03:29:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-calls-un-anti-israeli-body-as-un-chief-guterres-visits-gaza-border/articleshow/108743229.cms</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥军队搜寻 24 名可能被绑架的受害者</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/mexican-forces-search-for-24-possible-kidnapping-victims/articleshow/108742900.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108742900.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;墨西哥锡那罗亚州当局目前正在寻找据报道被绑架的 24 人，以及已发现安全的其他 40 多人。锡那罗亚州州长鲁本·罗查·莫亚 (Ruben Rocha Moya) 透露，共有 66 人被绑架。已找到 42 名据称被绑架的人，其中包括 24 名成人和 18 名儿童。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 02:55:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/mexican-forces-search-for-24-possible-kidnapping-victims/articleshow/108742900.cms</guid></item><item><title>塞内加尔在经历多年危机后投票选出新总统</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/senegal-votes-for-new-president-after-years-of-crisis/articleshow/108742977.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108742977.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;塞内加尔在经历了多年的动荡之后，本周日将在一场备受关注的选举中选举新总统。该国拥有 730 万选民，将前总理阿马杜·巴 (Amadou Ba) 和局外人巴西鲁·迪奥马耶·法耶 (Bassirou Diomaye Faye) 视为最有力的竞争者。 62 岁的 Ba 都是前税务检查员，他提供了连续性，与 43 岁的 Faye 的重大变革承诺和左翼泛非理想形成鲜明对比。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 03:21:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/senegal-votes-for-new-president-after-years-of-crisis/articleshow/108742977.cms</guid></item><item><title>音乐厅大屠杀后俄罗斯全国哀悼日</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/national-day-of-mourning-in-russia-after-concert-hall-massacre/articleshow/108742815.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108742815.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;莫斯科音乐厅发生悲惨事件后，俄罗斯将于周日举行全国哀悼日，伊斯兰国 (IS) 组织声称声称这是欧洲最严重的袭击事件，造成 130 多人丧生。俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京承诺追究那些对“野蛮恐怖袭击”负责的人的责任，并透露四名试图逃往乌克兰的枪手已被逮捕。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 02:49:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/national-day-of-mourning-in-russia-after-concert-hall-massacre/articleshow/108742815.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京的乌克兰计划是应对莫斯科袭击的核心</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putins-ukraine-plan-at-heart-of-response-to-moscow-attack/articleshow/108742510.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108742510.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在一场震惊莫斯科的悲惨事件中，俄罗斯对二十多年来最致命的恐怖袭击表示哀悼，随着救援行动的持续进行，死亡人数上升至 133 人。总统弗拉基米尔·普京在全国广播中透露，四名涉嫌前往乌克兰的嫌疑人被捕，但他没有直接暗示乌克兰政府。</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 02:03:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putins-ukraine-plan-at-heart-of-response-to-moscow-attack/articleshow/108742510.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>